    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<h1 dir=\"ltr\">Cheer Me On SPELL 2</h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">[Dynamic Heightening][Enchantment][Emotion]</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Traditions occult, primal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cast [two-actions] somatic, verbal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Range 30 feet; Target one creature</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Duration sustained up to one minute</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The creature you specify becomes attuned to the cheering of their allies, warding away fatigue and pains. Anyone within 30 feet of the target can take an audible, mental [one-action] action to call out encouragingly to the target while the spell persists, restoring [[/r 12[mental]]] hit points. Once a creature has cheered a creature on, they can't do so again for that creature until the start of their next turn.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The hit points restored increases by 6.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+1) </strong>The duration of the spell is no longer sustained and is just one minute.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> An additional target can be specified.</p>",
